{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2019-09-22-react-modal-with-form.markdown/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"前情提要\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E6%83%85%E6%8F%90%E8%A6%81\" aria-label=\"前情提要 permalink\" class=\"toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>前情提要</h1>\n<p>最近有个需求，需要在modal，提交多个表单数据，有点类似录入多条信息。这个需求的难点，在于如果获取到所有表单的数据。</p>\n<h1 id=\"过程\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B\" aria-label=\"过程 permalink\" class=\"toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>过程</h1>\n<p>在ant design的文档中，只发现了提交单个表单的数据的<a href=\"https://ant.design/components/form-cn/#components-form-demo-form-in-modal\">例子</a>，从这个例子中我们可以看到\n一个关键的属性<code class=\"language-text\">wrappedComponentRef</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"wrappedcomponentref\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#wrappedcomponentref\" aria-label=\"wrappedcomponentref permalink\" class=\"toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>wrappedComponentRef</h2>\n<p>看<a href=\"https://github.com/react-component/form/blob/master/src/createBaseForm.js\">源码</a>不难发现，它是组件的一个属性，用于获取form的ref，然后拿到form的实例，然后可以进行获取value</p>\n<h2 id=\"方案\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88\" aria-label=\"方案 permalink\" class=\"toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>方案</h2>\n<p>将form放在一个数组里，然后按添加按钮的时候往数组添加一个值，然后渲染数据时，遍历数组就行，同时使用wrappedComponentRef把form的实例绑定当前的组件上。</p>\n<h2 id=\"code-example\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#code-example\" aria-label=\"code example permalink\" class=\"toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>code example</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://codesandbox.io/embed/inspiring-oskar-4nlpr\">demo</a></p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E6%83%85%E6%8F%90%E8%A6%81\">前情提要</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B\">过程</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#wrappedcomponentref\">wrappedComponentRef</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88\">方案</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#code-example\">code example</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"ant design的modal中使用多个form表单","date":"2019-09-22 11:34:52 +0800"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2019-09-22-react-modal-with-form.markdown"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3649515864"],"slicesMap":{}}